---
import Breadcrumbs from '../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro'
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---
<Layout title="Accessibility | Rank4AI" description="Accessibility statement for Rank4AI.">
<section class="pt-12 pb-24">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[
      { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
      { label: 'Accessibility' }
    ]} />

    <h1 class="mb-6">Accessibility</h1>

    <img src="/images/content/ai-search-signals.svg" alt="AI search visibility signals" class="w-full rounded-xl mb-8 mt-6" loading="lazy">
    <div class="prose max-w-none text-[15px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
      <p>Rank4AI is committed to making our website accessible to all users. We aim to meet WCAG 2.1 Level AA standards.</p>
      <h2>What We Do</h2>
      <p>Our website uses semantic HTML, clear heading hierarchy, sufficient colour contrast, keyboard navigation support, alt text on images, and responsive design that works across devices.</p>
      <h2>Known Limitations</h2>
      <p>Some older content may not fully meet accessibility standards. We are working to address these as part of our ongoing site improvements.</p>
      <h2>Feedback</h2>
      <p>If you experience any accessibility issues, please contact us at info@rank4ai.co.uk and we will work to resolve them.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-off-white border-t border-border text-center py-16 px-10 mt-16">
    <a href="/free-audit/" class="cta-primary">Get a Free AI Search Visibility Audit &rarr;</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
